item.title: Went to climbing gym with Lin yesterday
item.description: 16:17 Sunday 05 July 2015 JST For our fourth anniversary, we went to a climbing gym near our house. Lin told all her co-workers how romantic I am and she thought of the idea and researched the location. We had a fun climbing and watching a young boy be taught how to climb (and respect his teacher). I got a few rips on my fingers from gripping the easy level grips on the walls which ranged from 85 degrees to 120 degrees.
